    textContent:
      "5.8          Vision Targets 5.8          Vision Targets The Upper\nHub is marked with a single 360° vision target consisting of 5 in.\n(~13 cm) long strips of 2 in. (~5 cm) wide 3M 8830 Scotchlite™\nReflective Material. A sample of the material is included in each Rookie\nKickoff Kit and FIRST Choice. The target is a 4\nft. 5⅜ in. (~136 cm) diameter ring of plastic with 16 strips\nadhered to it with 5½ in. (~14 cm) gaps between them. The ring is aligned such\nthat 1 of the gaps is centered over each UPPER EXIT.\nThe distance from FIELD carpet to the top of the target assembly is 8 ft. 8 in.\n(~264 cm); the distance from field carpet to\nthe bottom of the vision tape is 8 ft. 5⅝ in. (~258 cm).  Figure 5‑32: Vision target ",
