        text: "During the Playoff Matches, extra\nteam members may be needed to maintain the Robot\nbetween Matches because of the distance between\nthe Field and the pit area. Each team is\npermitted to have 3 additional pit crew members who can also help with needed Robot repairs/maintenance.",
        type: "text",
