    text: '<p class="RuleNumber-GameRulesRobot"><a name="G404"></a><b><span style="color:#1E5AA8">G404</span></b><b><span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\ncolor:#1E5AA8">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span class="Headline">Don’t hoard opposing </span><span class="GlossaryTerm-Headline">Cargo</span><span class="Headline">.</span></b> A <span class="GlossaryTerm">Robot</span> may not\nrestrict access to more than 3 opposing <span class="GlossaryTerm">Alliance</span>\n<span class="GlossaryTerm">Cargo</span> except during the final 30 seconds of the\n<span class="GlossaryTerm">Match</span>. </p><p class="Violation">Violation: <span class="GlossaryTerm"><i>Foul</i></span>, plus\nan additional <span class="GlossaryTerm"><i>Tech Foul</i></span> for every 5\nseconds in which the situation is not corrected.</p><div style="border:solid #0DBDD4 1.5pt;padding:0in 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\nmargin-left:.75in;margin-right:.75in">\n\n<p class="BlueBox" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in"><span style="color:black">Examples of restricting access to <span class="GlossaryTerm">Cargo</span> includes, but are not limited to,</span></p>\n\n<p class="BlueBox-LetteredList" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.25in"><span style="color:black;mso-color-alt:\nwindowtext">a.</span><span style="font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\ncolor:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color:black">holding 2 opposing <span class="GlossaryTerm">Alliance</span>\n<span class="GlossaryTerm">Cargo</span> within your <span class="GlossaryTerm">Robot</span>\nand blocking an opponent from getting to 2 more opposing <span class="GlossaryTerm">Alliance</span> <span class="GlossaryTerm">Cargo</span>\ncornered behind your <span class="GlossaryTerm">Robot</span>, or </span></p>\n\n<p class="BlueBox-LetteredList" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.25in"><span style="color:black;mso-color-alt:\nwindowtext">b.</span><span style="font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\ncolor:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color:black">using <span class="GlossaryTerm">Hangar</span> contact\nprotection afforded per G208-A to prevent an opponent from legally reaching 4\nopposing <span class="GlossaryTerm">Alliance</span> <span class="GlossaryTerm">Cargo</span>\ncornered in the back of your <span class="GlossaryTerm">Hangar</span>.</span></p>\n\n<p class="BlueBox" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in"><span style="color:black">In a scenario where a <span class="GlossaryTerm">Robot</span> is <span class="GlossaryTerm">Pinning</span> (per\nG202), <span class="GlossaryTerm">Referees</span> are instructed to disregard\nthis rule so they can focus on the <span class="GlossaryTerm">Pinning</span>.</span></p>\n\n</div>',
