    text: '<p class="RuleNumber-GameRulesHumans-Evergreen"><a name="H308"></a><b><span style="color:#3C7B3B">H308</span></b><b><span style="font-size:7.0pt;\nline-height:106%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;color:#3C7B3B">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span><span class="Headline-Evergreen">*Don’t bang on the glass.</span> </b>Team\nmembers may never strike or hit the <span class="GlossaryTerm">Driver Station</span>\nplastic windows.</p><p class="Violation">Violation: Verbal warning. If subsequent violations in more\nthan 1 <span class="GlossaryTerm"><i>Match</i></span>, <span class="GlossaryTerm"><i>Yellow\nCard</i></span>.</p>',
