    text: '<p class="RuleNumber-Robot-Evergreen"><a name="_Ref50390804"></a><a name="R405"></a><b><span style="color:#3C7B3B">R405</span></b><b><span style="font-size:7.0pt;\nline-height:106%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;color:#3C7B3B">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span><span class="Headline-EvergreenGlossaryterm">*Bumpers</span><span class="Headline-Evergreen"> indicate your </span><span class="Headline-EvergreenGlossaryterm">alliance</span><span class="Headline-Evergreen">.</span></b> Each <span class="GlossaryTerm">Robot</span>\nmust be able to display red or blue <span class="GlossaryTerm">Bumpers</span> to\nreflect their <span class="GlossaryTerm">Alliance</span> color, as assigned in\nthe <span class="GlossaryTerm">Match</span> schedule distributed at the event (as\ndescribed in <a href="#_Match_Schedules">Section 11.1 <span class="GlossaryTermInLink">Match</span> Schedules</a>). <span class="GlossaryTerm">Bumper</span>\nmarkings visible when installed on the <span class="GlossaryTerm">Robot</span>,\nother than the following, are prohibited:</p><p class="MsoListParagraph">A.<span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>those\nrequired per R406,</p><p class="MsoListParagraph">B.<span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>hook-and-loop\ntape or snap fasteners backed by the hard parts of the <span class="GlossaryTerm">Bumper</span>,</p><p class="MsoListParagraph">C.<span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>solid\nwhite <i>FIRST</i> logos between 4¾ in. (~12 cm) and 5¼ in. wide (~13 cm) (i.e.\ncomparable to those available in the <a href="https://www.firstinspires.org/robotics/frc/kit-of-parts#VirtualKit">RAPID\nREACT Virtual Kit</a>), and </p><p class="MsoListParagraph">D.<span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>narrow\nareas of underlying fabric exposed at seams, corners, or folds.</p><div style="border:solid #0DBDD4 1.5pt;padding:0in 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\nmargin-left:.75in;margin-right:.75in">\n\n<p class="BlueBox" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in"><span style="color:black">The <span class="GlossaryTerm">Frame\nPerimeter</span> facing surfaces of <span class="GlossaryTerm">Bumpers</span> are\nnot “displayed” and thus R405 does not apply.</span></p>\n\n</div>',
