    text: '<p class="RuleNumber-Robot-Evergreen"><a name="R904"></a><b><span style="color:\n#3C7B3B">R904</span></b><b><span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;color:#3C7B3B">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span><span class="Headline-Evergreen">*</span><span class="Headline-EvergreenGlossaryterm">Operator console</span><span class="Headline-Evergreen"> physical requirements.</span></b> The <span class="GlossaryTerm">Operator Console</span> must not </p><p class="MsoListParagraph">A.<span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>be longer\nthan 5 ft. (~152 cm), </p><p class="MsoListParagraph">B.<span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>be deeper\nthan 1 ft. 2 in. (~35 cm) (excluding any items that are held or worn by the <span class="GlossaryTerm">Drivers</span> during the <span class="GlossaryTerm">Match</span>),</p><p class="MsoListParagraph">C.<span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>extend\nmore than 6 ft. 6 in. (~198 cm) above the floor, or</p><p class="MsoListParagraph">D.<span style="font-size:7.0pt;line-height:106%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>attach to\nthe <span class="GlossaryTerm">Field</span> (except as permitted by G301).</p><div style="border:solid #0DBDD4 1.5pt;padding:0in 4.0pt 1.0pt 4.0pt;\nmargin-left:.75in;margin-right:.75in">\n\n<p class="BlueBox" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in"><span style="color:black">There is a 4 ft. 6 in. (~137 cm)\nlong by 2 in. (nominal) wide strip of hook-and-loop tape (“loop” side) along\nthe center of the <span class="GlossaryTerm">Driver Station</span> support shelf that\nshould be used to secure the <span class="GlossaryTerm">Operator Console</span>\nto the shelf, per G301. See <a href="#_Player_Driver_Station"><span class="GlossaryTerm"><span style="color:black">Driver Station</span></span></a><span class="GlossaryTerm"> </span>for details.</span></p>\n\n<p class="BlueBox" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in"><span style="color:black">Please note that while there is no\nhard weight limit, <span class="GlossaryTerm">Operator Consoles</span> that weigh\nmore than 30 lbs. (~13 kg.) will invite extra scrutiny as they are likely to\npresent unsafe circumstances. </span></p>\n\n</div>',
